sub_title: Kotlin | Java |  Spring Boot | AWS Certified Developer  | Azure | Design & Develop REST API | Agile
summary:
An Agile experienced Software Engineer with proven industry experience in cloud-based Java and Node.js software development. Enthusiastic about my work and always willing to go above and beyond to reach my goals. I have expertise in Java, Kotlin, Spring Boot, REST API, GraphQL, Docker, AWS, Azure, PCF and am constantly learning and adapting to new technologies to stay at the forefront of the industry. My goal is to create high-quality software solutions that meet the needs of businesses and users alike.

I am a team player who values open communication and collaboration, and I am always eager to learn new technologies and improve my skills. If you are looking for a Full Stack Developer who can help take your project to the next level, please don't hesitate to reach out.

For my next project, I'd like to work on low-latency applications requiring a high degree of scalability and resiliency, preferably running on a public cloud.
